snippet.title: Johnny Depp wins a victory in ongoing legal battle with ex-wife Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has been granted a motion to establish whether or not his ex-wife Amber Heard did donate her $7 million divorce settlement to charity.
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
